Oh I liked - we liked school. Yes. I - I enjoyed school. As long as we got on with the masters. Mr Wood was a very severe master. If you'd any - any - anything going - going on wrong, they - he'd b}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid3811210\charrsid8465662 e round with a smack for you. Yes}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid9710026\charrsid8465662 ? H}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid3811210\charrsid8465662 e\rquote }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid9710026\charrsid8465662 d keep you in order. But he was a good teacher.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid16396271 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid9710026\charrsid8465662 What did you feel about your teachers generally?
