Only if we were - if - if we weren't attending to then - all that he was saying to us when they were }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid3811210\charrsid8465662 teaching}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid9710026\charrsid8465662  - then - t
hen we should get - be in for it. But a good teacher, he get - kept your attention, you - respected him and you paid attention to him. When I was in the third or fourth standard we were having a lesson on geography, and we got a map of 
{\*\xmlopen\xmlns2{\factoidname place}}{\*\xmlopen\xmlns2{\factoidname country-region}}India{\*\xmlclose}{\*\xmlclose} on - on - pinn
ed onto the board. And Mr Bocock was the teacher then, he pointed at these - all the towns out all round the - all round the Indian coast, all the chief towns. And he says, as soon as any of you boys can come and - point out these - these - on the board c
ome forward - to the front, same as he'd been doing, and go through them, all the - all the towns, we could go home. And we - I can still remember them towns today. Pshaw, Willowhall, Hydrobad and {\*\xmlopen\xmlns2{\factoidname place}}
{\*\xmlopen\xmlns2{\factoidname City}}Karachi{\*\xmlclose}{\*\xmlclose}. {\*\xmlopen\xmlns2{\factoidname place}}{\*\xmlopen\xmlns2{\factoidname City}}Bombay{\*\xmlclose}{\*\xmlclose}, Gall, Calicott and Hydrobad. Columbo, Candi
, Ponticherry, Point de Galle. Pshaw, Willowhall, Hydrobad, {\*\xmlopen\xmlns2{\factoidname place}}{\*\xmlopen\xmlns2{\factoidname City}}Karachi{\*\xmlclose}{\*\xmlclose}. Agridelli. And I could point all those towns out round the coast of 
{\*\xmlopen\xmlns2{\factoidname country-region}}India{\*\xmlclose} and {\*\xmlopen\xmlns2{\factoidname place}}{\*\xmlopen\xmlns2{\factoidname country-region}}Ceylon{\*\xmlclose}{\*\xmlclose}
. Aye, well - it did - only - only a young boy at - at that age you know, but that's what he did. First - first inducement I've ever had like it - in - that we had to get on with the work. And I kept at school }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid7820956\charrsid8465662 \lquote }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid9710026\charrsid8465662 til I was at - in the ex seventh.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid16396271 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid9710026\charrsid8465662 Did your parents show an interest in your schoolwork?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid15152807 FT  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid9710026\charrsid8465662 Oh yes, they did. Oh yes, they - they - we had ex
aminations you know. Had to have - have the results of the exams - had to come home.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid16396271 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid9710026\charrsid8465662 
Did they ask you what you did at school and how you went on and that sort of thing?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid15152807 FT  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid9710026\charrsid8465662 Well, they knew what we were going - what we were doing, they kept in touch 
