 tested all our works, we were examined by the teachers. When we were young they came round to the desks, following you about and showing you all about it. But when we were - older, well our - results had to go - to
 them and they - took them home and marked them and give - give you certain marks for - for your work. Then they could see how far you were advanced you see and - how to treat you next day.
