{\*\xmlopen\xmlns2{\factoidname PlaceName}}High{\*\xmlclose} {\*\xmlopen\xmlns2{\factoidname PlaceType}}Grade school{\*\xmlclose}{\*\xmlclose} at night to learn shorthand and French - after I'd finished. At the other school.
