Twelve to begin with. But I only was sent - sent to - work for a fortnight and they only gave me two shillings a week and I'd got to walk from {\*\xmlopen\xmlns2{\factoidname address}}{\*\xmlopen\xmlns2{\factoidname Street}}Brunswick Place{\*\xmlclose}
{\*\xmlclose} to Stoke to where Boardhouse was, its a shipping agents. And then mother said, you're not going to go anymore, she said, it isn't paying your shoe leather. So she said - sent me back to school again 'til I was thirteen.
