\ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid9710026\charrsid8465662  to the ex-seventh standard.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid16396271 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid9710026\charrsid8465662 So you couldn't stay any longer at that school?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid15152807 FT  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid9710026\charrsid8465662 I couldn't stay any longer at tha
t school, no. So - so I went to work then you see. And then it was just in my own time later on that I went to learn shorthand and French When I needed them you see.
