I stayed - I stayed there - 'til 1939. When this house was built. And I came here after that.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid16396271 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid9710026\charrsid8465662 How old was your wife when you married?
