\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid15152807 FT  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid9710026\charrsid8465662 
Right up to the time we were married but not after. No. She was teaching right up to the time. Yes. In {\*\xmlopen\xmlns2{\factoidname place}}Lancashire{\*\xmlclose}. Not in our district.
