s - always teaching. And I used to visit her there and she'd come to our house when we were at {\*\xmlopen\xmlns2{\factoidname address}}{\*\xmlopen\xmlns2{\factoidname Street}}Brunswick Place{\*\xmlclose}{\*\xmlclose}
, to visit - our - my people you see, when we had an opportunity.
