\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid15152807 FT  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid9710026\charrsid8465662 
What, when she was at the - teaching? Oh she was very happy in her work. I - I met several of her friends like from the college. Yes, oh yes, she - had quite a nice lot of friends at the college. And some of them came to this area - area, during the war.

\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid16396271 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid9710026\charrsid8465662 You had two children?
