ame as we did. We - we - we - as I say, we didn't - we weren't tyrants. We - we loved them and they loved us. We helped one another. And you talk to one another about anything.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid16396271 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid9710026\charrsid8465662 What did you bring then up to consider important in life?
