, was the only magazines, what you call a magazine. Christian Herald,
 it was - it was once a week, the Christian Herald. And we had the Sentinel, but the Sentinel was - was not a lot of rubbish in it same as it is now, only a few - few pages in the Sentinel. My mother used to read from beginning to end of the Sentinel, so 
shows you just - only a small little - little paper in those days.
