\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid15152807 FT  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid9710026\charrsid8465662 Both of us, yes. And it isn't often I w
as by myself, my wife was used - we were all four together as a rule. But sometimes I'd be out with the children only. Specially when they got older. Used to walk all round Badley Edge and - Standley, all about the neighbour - Birch's Head neighbourhood. 
{\*\xmlopen\xmlns2{\factoidname place}}{\*\xmlopen\xmlns2{\factoidname City}}Stanley{\*\xmlclose}{\*\xmlclose}
 Pool, yes. Then - my father's mother lived at Badley Edge for some years. As well. And we used to visit them there. And along - along with an aunt - two aunts.
