{\*\xmlopen\xmlns2{\factoidname place}}{\*\xmlopen\xmlns2{\factoidname City}}Alice{\*\xmlclose}{\*\xmlclose}, I looked after myself. Oh I can - always capable of looking after myself. But the - when I was at - at business, if the - if 
{\*\xmlopen\xmlns2{\factoidname place}}{\*\xmlopen\xmlns2{\factoidname City}}Alice{\*\xmlclose}{\*\xmlclose} wasn't well then this neighbour would come in to see to her you see.
